metadata.name: Try the devil!
metadata.description:
Yuyuan Woke up.



The first thing he saw was the half-naked regular-autumn Boat in the cold stone chamber.



Looking at the lines of ice silver chains tied to the boat, he frowned and subconsciously said: "You, too, were imprisoned by the Han Yin Clan? How long have I been here?"



Just calm soon regulus autumn Fang, heard his words, strange expression.
